list.name: Changes
list.comment: Stage 4: Fleshed out the Knight class, that should be mostly done for now. Added exclusion for certain columns due to the way I am calculating legal moves, will be adding more of those types of things to the BoardUtils class. Also changed the "list" of moves from an actual List to a Collection, as it makes more sense for Chess. Moved some declarations around as well. I think it is using more memory this way, but it's cleaner code so it works for me.

task.summary: Stage 2: still the tile class. added as much immutability as I could for the purposes of learning. it makes sense as well since chess is a very strict game. imported google's Guava libary to use ImmutableMap. Also got 99 fishing in OSRS earlier today! :)
